- I was a beat reporter
covering City Hall.

00:30.321 --> 00:31.990
Yes, you were.

00:32.073 --> 00:34.284
- And I was on the sports desk
covering baseball.
- Football.

00:34.367 --> 00:35.827
Right, right, right.

00:35.910 --> 00:37.996
- For three years, we never met.
- Three whole years.

00:38.079 --> 00:40.039
Then one day, I was
on the F train
to get a blowout,

00:40.123 --> 00:42.667
and Metallo derailed my train.
Sent it airborne.

00:42.751 --> 00:46.588
So I, uh... [laughs]
So I caught that train
and set it down

00:46.671 --> 00:48.965
on top of the LexCorp building
just to talk to her.

00:49.048 --> 00:50.300
Yes, you did.

00:50.383 --> 00:51.718
