[Harley]<i> Holy shit.</i>
<i>Do I love Valentine's Day?</i>

01:02.020 --> 01:05.398
<i>Not only is it the gushiest,</i>
<i>mushiest, most romantic</i>
<i>day of the year,</i>

01:05.482 --> 01:07.525
