<i>you have a bulletproof excuse</i>

01:07.609 --> 01:11.821
<i>for doing super cheesy shit</i>
<i>for your partner.</i>

01:11.905 --> 01:15.033
<i>You can eat as much chocolate</i>
<i>as you want, no judgment.</i>

01:15.116 --> 01:17.076
<i>And it's super fucking</i>
<i>cold in February,</i>

01:17.160 --> 01:21.247
<i>so it's the perfect</i>
<i>excuse to snuggle.</i>

01:21.331 --> 01:24.751
